# (also-gitignored) full slim cache in ThaqalaynDataGenerator/tmp/.
sources/wiktextract-arabic/wiktextract_corpus_lemmas.json

# hawramani raw HTML dump — 140+ MB across thousands of small files,
# noisy from a code-review POV. The structured hawramani_entries.json
# committed alongside is the load-bearing artifact. Regenerable by:
#   python scripts/scrape_hawramani.py --full
# and then:
#   python scripts/build_hawramani_structured.py
sources/hawramani-classical/raw/

